bcid
Class BCIDMetadataSchema

java.lang.Object
  bcid.BCIDMetadataSchema
Direct Known Subclasses:
Renderer
public class BCIDMetadataSchema
extends java.lang.Object

Metadata Schema for Describing an identifier -- These are the metadata elements building blocks that we can use to express this identifier either via RDF or HTML and consequently forms the basis of what the "outside" world sees about the identifiers. This class is used by Renderers to structure content.
